title: Call of Duty 4 Mac 1.x to 1.7b patcher including nocd-crack
description:
Version 1.7.1b (added option to browse for destination)


This file contains an installer to patch Call of Duty 4 version 1.x to version 1.7.

The installer was created because of large scale installation problems in the 

original installer created by Aspyr Media.

The installer was build using VISE X

The installer also contains the 1.5 no-cd crack for the Mac single player version.

This installer is virus-free and comes as-is without any support.
